        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-b66d1394-bdc2-40c4-a090-bad34d5489b8'>
            
<p class="">gamated during the past five years with departments for older children; how many new combined departments for infants and juniors have been opened in the same period of time; and how many of both types of combined departments are in charge of men and women head-teachers, respectively?</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
